    ApplicationRegistration, SocialAgentRegistration
    public abstract class AgentRegistration
extends CRUDResource
    Abstract base instantiation of a modifiable Agent Registration, which can be extended for type-specific implementations (i.e. Social Agent Registration, Application Registration).
